        "timezone": "Europe/Rome",
        "scraping_time": "2025-03-24T04.00.16",
        "en_title": "Idf, 'in the hospital Nasser hit terrorist Hamas key'",
        "en_content": "\"Poo do, Idf and Isa (Shin Bet)\nhit a key terrorist with precision\nin the Hamas terrorist organization that was operating\ninside the complex of the Nasser hospital.\" It refers\nIdf confirming the raid on the structure at Khan Yunis.\n\n\n\"The attack was conducted following a wide process of\ncollection of information and with precise ammunition in order to\nmitigate damage as much as possible,\" continues Idf adding\nthat \"Hamas exploits civil infrastructure while putting\nbrutally in danger the people of Gaza.\"\n\n\nMeanwhile, Al Jazeera reports that at least five\nPalestinians were killed and others were injured in\nbombing. According to the Palestinian agency Wafa, in the raid is\nhit the second floor of the complex \"trying fires\nand causing the death and wounding of many citizens.\"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nReproduction reserved © Copyright ANSA\n\n\n\n",
        "en_subtitle": "Israel confirms responsibility. At Jazeera, at least 5 dead",
